  "original_title": "1.7 \u0b95\u0bcb\u0b9f\u0bbf \u0bb0\u0bc2\u0baa\u0bbe \u0baa\u0bc6\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0bae\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe\u0ba9 \u0bb5\u0bc6\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0ba8\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0ba3\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc8 \u0b89\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc2\u0bb2\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b85\u0ba9\u0bc1\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa \u0bb5\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4 \u0b87\u0bb3\u0bc8\u0b9e\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A young man was arrested for sending foreign currency worth Rs 1.7 crore through money order",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "A young man was arrested with foreign currency notes worth Rs 1.7 crore, police said.",
        "A 27-year-old youth has been arrested with foreign currency notes worth Rs 1.7 crore in Weligama area.",
        "Initial investigations by the police revealed that the said youth was keeping the money to be sent abroad through the money order system.",
        "Following a tip-off, the police raided a house in Welikamai area and found foreign currency notes.",
        "18,208 US Dollars, 20,035 Euros, 645 Sri Lankan Pounds, 100,000 Japanese Yen, 1,000 Qatari Riyals and 18,500 Dirhams were recovered in this way.",
        "The police said that the arrested youth, a suspect from Weligama Kalpoka area, will be produced in the Matara Magistrate's Court after further investigations."
      ],
